{
  "id": "adv_main_02_01_00",
  "title": "東京編1章",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_home_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――NEXT VENUSグランプリ決勝から数ヶ月後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several months after the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix finals",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 2.47
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（みんなで東京に出て来て）\n（まだ数ヶ月なんだよな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It’s only been a few months）\n（since we all moved to Tokyo.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.033333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（まさかこんなことになるなんて……信じられるか？）\n（お前がいたら何て言うかな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I had no idea things would turn out this way… Can you believe it?）\n（I wonder what you’d say if you were here.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6133.333333333337,
          "startTime": 22.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_stm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 23.866666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！\nあれ？　なにぼーっとしてるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nHuh? What are you looking at?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ橋本さん\nちょっとグランプリの映像を見返してたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Hashimoto-san.\nI was looking over the footage from the Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！　もしかして、現実逃避というやつでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah! Could it be an escape from reality?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "違うよ、そういう訳じゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's not like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、私も星見プロに入社してからの\n怒涛の日々には驚いてるので、お気持ちは分かります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ I'm also surprised by the hectic days\nsince joining Hoshimi Pro. I understand how you feel!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロもやらかしちゃったし\n目まぐるしいですもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and also the Van Pro. messed up.\nEverything is just so chaotic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-stm005.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れですよね……でも！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It must be exhausting… But!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-stm006.m4a",
      "text": "これから私たちは、並みいる強豪をバッタバッタと\nなぎ倒してトップアイドルを目指していくんですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From now on‚ we'll knock down all the strong rivals\nand aim to be the top idols!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-stm007.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロの大進撃でアイドル業界を\n「あっ！」と言わせてやりましょー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's make the idol industry go\n\"Ah!\" with Hoshimi Pro's major offensive!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよな、止まってる場合じゃない。ありがとう\nそれより、なにか用があったんじゃ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ you're right. There's no time to stop. Thanks.\nBy the way‚ did you have something to discuss?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-stm008.m4a",
      "text": "あー！　そうです！\n{user}さんを呼びに来たんでした！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! That's right!\nI came to call {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-stm009.m4a",
      "text": "今日は久しぶりのミーティングですし\n先ほどから、オフィスでお待ちしていますよー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been a while since our meeting today.\nEveryone have been waiting for you at the office!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-stm010.m4a",
      "text": "新人アイドルのトップをひた走る、あの十七人が！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The seventeen‚ running at the top of the rookie idols‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-stm011.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……尊いなぁ……！　私なんて、あのメンバーが\n一堂に会するだけで目が潰れちゃいそうですもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "you know…Hah….so precious…! Even just for me\nto see them all together‚ my eyes might explode.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "入社してしばらく経つのに、まだ慣れないのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been a while since you joined‚ and still not used to it…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-stm012.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよねぇ。そろそろ仕事に支障を\nきたしそうで……そんなことより！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true. It might start affecting my work…\nBut more importantly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-stm013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも早くみなさんの\n素敵な笑顔を見に行きましょー！　御開帳～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ let's go see everyone's wonderful smiles quickly!\nOpen the curtains~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 118.26666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、代理とはいえ\n今は代表なんですから、遅刻はよくないと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ even though you're filling in as a substitute‚\nyou're the representative now‚ so being late isn't good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "もう琴乃ちゃん、{user}さんの体調\nさっきまであんなに心配してたのにね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ you were so worried\nabout {user}-san's health just now…right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます！\nみんな集まるとなんだか大家族みたいで楽しいですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning! When everyone gathers‚\nit feels like a big family and it's fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっさくらちゃん\n朝からすごく楽しみにしていたものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ Sakura-chan‚\nyou are so excited starting from the morning~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です。{user}さん\n久しぶりに全員集まりましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ {user}-san.\nWe've gathered together after a long time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "ほんま賑やかやなぁ。バンプロの時はグループ同士\nもうちょいギスギスしてた気するわぁ。なぁ莉央さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's sure lively here‚ ain't it? Back in Van Production‚\nthe groups were a tad more uptight. Ain't that right‚ Rio-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "私達だって別に仲悪くもなかったでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We weren't really on bad terms either‚ were we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "でもさすがに、これだけ集まると騒がしいわ\nさっさと始めちゃいましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ indeed‚ it's noisy when this many people gather.\nLet's get started quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_00-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "僕も賛成",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I agree too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
